# VHS Demo: Transcript to Proposal Skill

Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 800
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 40

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 300ms

Type "# TRANSCRIPT → PROPOSAL"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "# ─────────────────────────"
Enter
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# INPUT:"
Enter
Type "#   product.md + transcript.md"
Enter
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# ANALYZE PAINS:"
Enter
Type "#   TRIGGER → 'deadline March 15'"
Enter
Type "#   ACTIVE  → 'mechanisms failing'"
Enter
Type "#   LATENT  → 'dated design'"
Enter
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# CHECKPOINT: confirm priorities"
Enter
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "# GENERATE:"
Enter
Type "#   proposal.md"
Enter
Type "#   architecture.md"
Enter
Type "#   prototype.html"
Enter
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# ─────────────────────────"
Enter
Type "# Client words → Professional proposal"
Enter
Sleep 2s
